description: Returns billable usage logs in CSV format for the specified account and date range.

YYYY-MM.description: . Last month to return billable usage logs for. This field is required.

false.description: Specify whether to include personally identifiable information in the billable usage logs, for example the email addresses of cluster creators. Handle this information with care. Defaults to false.

401.description: The request does not have valid authentication credentials for the operation.
